## Request Parameters
<a name="API_waf_DeleteRateBasedRule_RequestParameters"></a>

For information about the parameters that are common to all actions, see [Common Parameters](CommonParameters.md).

The request accepts the following data in JSON format.

 ** [ChangeToken](#API_waf_DeleteRateBasedRule_RequestSyntax) **   <a name="WAF-waf_DeleteRateBasedRule-request-ChangeToken"></a>
The value returned by the most recent call to [GetChangeToken](API_waf_GetChangeToken.md).  
Type: String  
Length Constraints: Minimum length of 1. Maximum length of 128.  
Pattern: `.*\S.*`   
Required: Yes

 ** [RuleId](#API_waf_DeleteRateBasedRule_RequestSyntax) **   <a name="WAF-waf_DeleteRateBasedRule-request-RuleId"></a>
The `RuleId` of the [RateBasedRule](API_waf_RateBasedRule.md) that you want to delete. `RuleId` is returned by [CreateRateBasedRule](API_waf_CreateRateBasedRule.md) and by [ListRateBasedRules](API_waf_ListRateBasedRules.md).  
Type: String  
Length Constraints: Minimum length of 1. Maximum length of 128.  
Pattern: `.*\S.*`   
Required: Yes

